<br />
<br />(use UDLR on controller to scroll)
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />Also, I want to make it so that the background initialization is done all in one pass... The problem is there is not enough vBlank time for that. Is there a way I can black the screen out and keep rendering without the PPU interfering?</div>

